<span style='float: right; width: 280px; height: 187px; margin: 0 0 5px 5px; border: 1px solid black;'><script type='text/javascript'>flash_object ('http://graphics.millsberry.com/buddy/buddy_featured_v14.swf', '280', '187', 'userName=bexbex815&buddyTimeStamp=20060824&buddyScriptURL=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.millsberry.com%2Fbuddy%2Fprocess_buddy.phtml&unixTimeStamp=1157231959&serverTimeOffset=28800', '', 'exactfit');</script></span>
Meet <b>Bexbexbex</b>, our citizen of the week!<br><br>Bexbexbex lives at <a href='/home/?user=bexbex815'>59918 Triumph Boulevard</a> in the trendy neighborhood of Metro Park.  She's been visiting the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/main_map.phtml?location=downtown">Downtown area</a>'s nearby shops almost every day since she first moved to Millsberry on June 3, 2006.<br><br>Bexbexbex has always been very friendly, and she has a rather unique way of breaking the ice when meeting new people &mdash; by doing a magic trick!  Bexbexbex's magic puts a smile on people's faces and makes them feel at ease with her right away.  That is just one example of Bexbexbex's cleverness and creativity, though.  Her smarts also extend to her academic studies, where she can usually be found at the head of her class, especially in foreign language courses.  Bexbexbex's favorite thing about learning a new language is that it allows her to make friends from all over the world!<br><br>Bexbexbex also has a wonderful sense of humor.  She loves to act, and her favorite roles are the comedic ones.  Bexbexbex has often said that the greatest feeling in the world is being onstage and hearing the audience roar with laughter as a result of her comic abilities.  As a way of studying her craft, Bexbexbex visits the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/complex/theater.phtml">theater</a> in the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/complex/">Downtown Entertainment Complex</a> several times a week to see all the latest comedy releases.<br><br>When Bexbexbex isn't catching a new film, she's most likely to be spotted at the mall, browsing the shelves in search of the best oldies, classic rock, and disco CDs, or at the <a href="http://www.millsberry.com/shop.phtml?shop_id=1">Clothing Store</a>, trying on the hottest light blue, pink, and zebra-striped fashions.  If Bexbexbex really wants to relax, she heads to her best friend's house, where they spend time writing comedy skits or practicing magic tricks together.<br><br>Thanks for being a good citizen, Bexbexbex, and congratulations on being named Millsberry's citizen of the week!</div>
